📌 What’s Changed?

Aspect	Before (JPA, Relational DB)	Now (Cosmos DB, NoSQL)
Annotations Used	@Entity, @Table, @OneToMany, @ManyToOne, @Enumerated	@Container, @PartitionKey
Relationship Mapping	@OneToMany, @ManyToOne	Replaced with List<>
Primary Key	@Id	Cosmos DB uses id field
Partitioning	N/A (handled by RDBMS)	@PartitionKey on key fields
JPA Repository	JpaRepository<PolicyHolder, String>	CosmosRepository<PolicyHolder, String>
SQL Queries	@Query annotations	Uses Cosmos SQL API



